FBIS4-18042 "drsov083_b_94026" FBIS-SOV-94-083 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Media Issues IZVESTIYA Announces New `Expert Assessment' Section IZVESTIYA Announces New `Expert Assessment' Section PM2704143794 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 27 Apr 94 p 1 PM2704143794 Moscow IZVESTIYA Russian BFN [Untitled editorial office announcement] [Text] This issue of our newspaper includes the new "pilot" insert "IZVESTIYA. Expert Assessment." It will carry articles by independent experts who will discuss how best to use vouchers in the days remaining until the end of voucher privatization; what will happen to crime in the immediate future; what is the quality of the drinking water we receive from city pipes; the dangers of domestic microwave ovens; why American consumers are not worried about the quality of their food and medicine; what a Snickers bar actually contains; how apartments are bought and sold; and much else besides.
